---
title: Sage-Butter Roasted Pork with Roasted Butternut Squash & Charred Broccolini
description: Sage adds earthy depth to honeyed squash and juicy pro chops in this Instgram-worth dish. Roasting the broccolini helps developed crispy edges and a nutty flavor - try with regular broccoli too!
